00:49:872 (49872|0,50590|3) - Wanna move to 里面，只是觉得不叠更贴合音乐

kiai of this diff should be buffed a bit considering the spread. Espeically comparing with Muzukashii, the density of the whole section of this diff and muzu is too similar (the difference of them is just Oni has some colour changes for 1/4s) and this is making the spread unbalanced. My suggestion here would be adding some more 1/4s during kiai, you can also use 5plet if you think it fits. Here are some examples to give you some ideas how to buff this section:
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/709366576448798750/1168171966679756911/image.png?ex=6550cbec&is=653e56ec&hm=a6f5c8eff913f19f9136435894d88c99d3a944a0080fd9d04151a906f949b387&)
![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/709366576448798750/1168172123680952320/image.png?ex=6550cc11&is=653e5711&hm=eb9f8af1b3e1d6646fd7e6e2dd7256b52cc42a65823768932e8bbb77023fcf5d&)
and be careful don't buff it too much and making it too similar with Inner.
